name: 10 Out Of 10 Dinosaurs
overview: For all ages of players. This package is the fun way to learn the truth about dinosaurs. The six games all have superb digitized graphics to make a whole area of history - dinosaurs - come alive. If you came face to face with a tyrannosaurus would you run away? Or are you safe because it's a vegetarian and wouldn't eat you? This, together with 100s of other interesting facts, can be discovered from this enthralling package. The six games - all with single and multi-player options - are educational fun for everyone.
